EASY BOOKING

How to Book


Please email hello@londoncatsitters.com

with the following information

your name

your full postcode

your phone number

the number of cats to be cared for

the requested booking dates

if you need one or two visits per day

any other useful information

We will respond within 24 hours with your

price per visit and to confirm availability.



WE TAKE CARE OF YOUR KITTENS AS IF THEY WERE OURS.
